cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with semantic indexing of image and video data, which is a problem in computer vision and multimedia analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses optimization techniques and parameter estimation, which are topics in machine learning and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The paper also deals with natural language processing and text-based indexing, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper discusses information retrieval, which is a topic in cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and multimedia analysis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
